data.description: New Price Adjustment! All offers will be presented to seller! Look no further this gorgeous home sits on 1.79 acres. it has 4bdr, 3 bath 2 car garage at 2,854 sq ft!  Kitchen was updated 5 yrs ago, backsplash, counter top, lighting. Crown molding in kitchen, dinning room and living room. You'll be envy of neighbors you have an oasis in your backyard they spared nothing on this  custom pool, jacuzzi spa with a waterfall! Patio was extended to hold huge parties. Still need more room this property has a huge 20 x 60 shop that was added. The bar area is 20 X 25 and has AC and heating! You say you need more storage for all your toys equipment you have  back of shop for that!
